{
  "stem": "43.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when she came with other child, [NON-ENGLISH], the two children were so crying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they-- the was sitting by the [NON-ENGLISH] under a closet in a-- and through the closet, she gave them eat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because she got a 13-year-old girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't want her, because her girl can-- can tell somebody but here is Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they would kill here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she give through the closet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She gave them in, right?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I came every night-- when I came, they-- there-- so she took time them out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The night, here-- here your girl was asleep already in another room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she took them out-- the-- the children for me, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she told me-- she told me all about, but my sisters wrote to me that please don't cry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you were able maybe to-- to-- to [NON-ENGLISH] two children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- the children was so crying after the little brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it didn't help us too much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And very soon, the Germans hang up papers of-- of houses, and not to give us Jew a piece of bread-- and not told.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If they will-- some in contact with Jews-- so they will kill them, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she told me she can't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She don't want to hold the two children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I was thinking-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I-- I was thinking what-- what-- what to do here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the other night came two boys-- my sister's-- one 13-years-old, and one-- and one around 16-years-old.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took-- they-- they took all of them from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One-- one is-- he fall also on the grave with a-- his family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every family is together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he came out in the night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was full of blood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he-- he came out.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
